## Wiki-T5 [G18] WikiView sidebar loads dual-region tree (Raw + Wiki) and filters by search
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `frontend/src/views/WikiView.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1, Wiki-D2

1. Render `<WikiView />` with mock API returning 3 pages
2. Assert sidebar shows 3 page items (title + tags)
3. Type search query matching only 1 page title
4. Assert sidebar filters to 1 item

- Page list loads from `GET /api/forge/wiki/{project}/pages`.
- Search input filters pages client-side by title and tags.

