## Wiki-T6 [G18] Clicking wiki page loads full content and renders markdown
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `frontend/src/views/WikiView.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1, Wiki-D2

1. Render `<WikiView />` with mocked `loadPage`
2. Click first page in sidebar
3. Assert `loadPage(project, slug)` called with correct slug
4. Assert `MarkdownContent` component renders with page content
5. Assert content header shows page title, source type badge, version

- Full page content loaded from `GET /api/forge/wiki/{project}/page/{slug}`.
- Markdown rendered via existing `MarkdownContent.vue`.

