## Wiki-T8 [G18] Create new page flow with path-based slug creates page and adds to tree
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `frontend/src/views/WikiView.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:both
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1, Wiki-D2

1. Render `<WikiView />`
2. Click "+" button in sidebar header
3. Fill slug, title, content in inline form
4. Click "Create"
5. Assert `createPage(project, page)` called with correct data
6. Assert new page appears in sidebar
7. Assert newly created page is selected and rendered

- Create flow calls `POST /api/forge/wiki/{project}/pages`.
- New page immediately appears in sidebar after creation.

