## Wiki-T9 [G18] Delete page removes from tree after confirmation
**Status:** done
**Test File:** `frontend/src/views/WikiView.vue` (component test)
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1, Wiki-D2

1. Render `<WikiView />`, select a page
2. Click "Delete" button
3. Assert confirmation dialog appears
4. Confirm deletion
5. Assert `deletePage(project, slug)` called
6. Assert page removed from sidebar
7. Assert empty state shown (no page selected)

- Delete calls `DELETE /api/forge/wiki/{project}/page/{slug}`.
- Confirmation dialog prevents accidental deletion.

